{"tid":1541044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[機會嚟喇!飛雲!脫亞入歐!] 默克爾聽日開始一連3日訪華，要爭取佢第三日7/9訪港，將救援消息推到德國同埋歐盟","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:30:45.000Z","uid":295732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"786010ba260af96818370d0c7efa3b72b0209751","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">默克爾明起訪華 德報：若中國不尊重港人權利 德國可給予港人難民名額</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%AF-%E5%BE%B7%E5%A0%B1-%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AF%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%2588%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25A1%258D%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=e88b07ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BA%2588%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25A1%258D%2F&h=19f01afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%AA%E8%8F%AF-%E5%BE%B7%E5%A0%B1-%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AF%E7%B5%A6%E4%BA%88%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D/</a><br />\n<br />\n叫佢第三天唔好去華中理工大學  直接到香港同居港德國人傾<br />\n<br />\n她的行程：<br />\n第一天李克強<br />\n第二天習近平<br />\n只有第三天比較有機會過來<br />\n而且佢會有自己的專機<br />\n<br />\n上邊個報導引用左世界報報導<br />\n1.世界報是全德大報，影響力唔輸南德日報跟法蘭克福廣訊報，總主筆都咁幫忙了。<br />\n<br />\n2.Bild就是德國蘋果日報，全德銷量第一，這幾天都配合刊出黃之鋒的公開信，德國公眾對於香港的關注這幾天是有所聚焦的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.目標就是9月7日邀請她不去武漢過來香港，香港會比華中理工大學重要多了。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4.還有一個很大的切入點，就是國泰的白色恐怖。默克爾這次是帶了商界人士去，英資的太古集團如何被中共白色恐怖搞，可以讓德國人知道，讓默克爾知道。像是國泰主席今天都辭任了，這個也是德國人會在意的點。七天前這一份新聞，國泰事件剛好是印證<span style=\"color: blue;\">歐洲企業的惡夢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n但如果叫佢直接訪港會太唐突，當然會見民間記者會就最好<br />\n<br />\n但係可以透過<br />\n德國駐港領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GermanConsulateGeneralHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGermanConsulateGeneralHongKong%2F&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=ecfb03a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GermanConsulateGeneralHongKong/</a><br />\n<br />\n用入面近期有嘅活動做原因:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/349406882636621/?event_time_id=349406892636620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F349406882636621%2F%3Fevent_time_id%3D349406892636620&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=b2b9fc5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/349406882636621/?event_time_id=349406892636620</a><br />\n居港的德國錄像藝術家和實驗電影人 Max Hattler 將在歌德藝廊展出其作品展 Receptive Rhythms 他的作品錯綜複雜，涵蓋動畫、錄像裝置和影音表演。展覽將於9月5日至28日於歌德藝廊展出。詳情請參看活動專頁。<br />\n歌德藝廊，是香港歌德學院的一部分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goethe.de/en/uun/akt/21486075.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goethe.de%2Fen%2Fuun%2Fakt%2F21486075.html&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=6c8184cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.goethe.de/en/uun/akt/21486075.html</a><br />\n<br />\n因為默克爾曾經訪日時去東京的歌德學院參訪<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goethe.de/en/uun/akt/21486075.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goethe.de%2Fen%2Fuun%2Fakt%2F21486075.html&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=6c8184cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.goethe.de/en/uun/akt/21486075.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而今次佢係帶埋商業團隊黎<br />\n就可以用埋中國個社會信用體系對外資嘅影響去令佢多個原因訪港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/外媒視點/369114/中國歐盟商會-社會信用體系也針對外國企業-分數決定命運\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E8%A6%96%E9%BB%9E%2F369114%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E4%B9%9F%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD-%E5%88%86%E6%95%B8%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%91%BD%E9%81%8B&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=f9c316f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/外媒視點/369114/中國歐盟商會-社會信用體系也針對外國企業-分數決定命運</a> &lt;-黨報慎入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推到攬炒巴見到，推到德國見到！[size=5]<br />\n[size=5]<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> Nach Freiheit ! ! ! </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7203fab560fcf592e3f0f8304bf96c4258303309","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"060e31085f6522f1c939e25866914d205c56300d","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"08fa78fba9e32caf8205366fbcc9ef0a91637200","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"009e9cbbeec70e39275ed065e8a59da42b5adc9c","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"3af310e73238b2149681cfb5caff9ba4fa495ddb","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"74a9c45e3c6607934c682332eaa3bb367a36e965","tid":1541044,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46fcfe25054044851ec20347752285b942dac139","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"eef3b6d5d62f02168b103fb2045dd1668f1a41c6","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"183c6676f256f33361836e9dc6107b56d8d553db","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"d50df31e50197581eea72e04487b5a562bbe3b2d","tid":1541044,"uid":295732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"推到默EE睇到"},{"pid":"2a77546c2ff4bf2154b98384bc8a13225a399d4f","tid":1541044,"uid":38055,"like":0,"dislike